item.title: CVE-2023-45798|2023-10-30T06:17:14.332Z -- yettiesoft -- vestcert
item.description: In Yettiesoft VestCert versions 2.36 to 2.5.29, a vulnerability exists due to improper validation of third-party modules. This allows malicious actors to load arbitrary third-party modules, leading to remote code execution.
